_sText:
My version of poolparty. I hope you guys enjoy. 

Features: 
New added hot tub
New lifeguard towers

Install:
Extract the map file (fy_poolparty_gpk.bsp), and the navigation file (many_houses_wcs.nav) to your Counter-Strike maps folder (Usually located here:C:\Program Files\steam\steamapps\***YOURNAMEHERE***\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps).

Author: GabrielPapaK

Time: 3 Hours

Hope you enjoy!
